channel.title: A server to play?
channel.description:
I'm not interested in Runescape or a private server with less than 200 people. I know SoulSplit has thousands playing and BattleScape is back up (for like the 6th time), but does anyone have any suggestions for a good quality server? Looking for older graphics preferably but not a requirement.
Also, if anyone wants to join me on playing an RSPS. I will be down. When I don't have homework or I'm not working I'm not sure what to do.
